<iproblem maxpoints="1"><vardef name="x" type="numeric" format="#"><constraint><range type="ge"><expr>2</expr></range><range type="le"><expr>12</expr></range></constraint></vardef><vardef name="y" type="numeric" format="#"><constraint><range type="ge"><expr>2</expr></range><range type="le"><expr>10</expr></range></constraint></vardef><vardef name="z" type="numeric" format="#"><constraint><range type="ge"><expr>3</expr></range><range type="le"><expr>10</expr></range></constraint></vardef><vardef name="a" type="numeric" format="#"><constraint><inclusion><expr>~z\+~x\</expr></inclusion></constraint></vardef><vardef name="b" type="numeric" format="#"><constraint><inclusion><expr>~z\-~x\</expr></inclusion></constraint></vardef><vardef name="c" type="numeric" format="#.#"><constraint><inclusion><expr>(~y\-1)/2</expr></inclusion></constraint></vardef><vardef name="d" type="numeric" format="#.#"><constraint><inclusion><expr>~y\-~c\</expr></inclusion></constraint></vardef>
	<iprostep id="step0" points="1">
		<div>
			<p>Match the inequalities with the corresponding statements:</p>
			<p>1. <iproformula alt=" " src="geteq.ashx?eqtext= a &amp;gt; ~x\" style="margin-bottom:-3px; vertical-align:middle" type="text" /></p>
			<p>2. <iproformula alt=" " src="geteq.ashx?eqtext=@abs{a-~y\} &amp;lt; @DIV{1;~x\} " style="margin-bottom:0px; vertical-align:middle" type="text" /></p>
			<p>3. <iproformula alt=" " src="geteq.ashx?eqtext=@abs{a-@DIV{1;~x\}} &amp;lt; ~y\" style="margin-bottom:0px; vertical-align:middle" type="text" /></p>
			<p>4. <iproformula alt=" " src="geteq.ashx?eqtext=@abs{a} &amp;gt; ~y\" style="margin-bottom:-3px; vertical-align:middle" type="text" /></p>
			<p>5. <iproformula alt=" " src="geteq.ashx?eqtext=@abs{a-~z\} &amp;lt; ~x\" style="margin-bottom:-3px; vertical-align:middle" type="text" /></p>
			<p>6. <iproformula alt=" " src="geteq.ashx?eqtext=1 &amp;lt; a &amp;lt; ~y\" style="margin-bottom:-3px; vertical-align:middle" type="text" /></p>
			<p>(Enter the number written by each inequality into the statement box.)</p>
			<p><iproelement_short correct="6" elid="1" format="" id="@step.s@id" size="2" tolerance="0.0" type="numeric" version="2" /> The distance from <iproformula alt=" " src="geteq.ashx?eqtext=a" style="margin-bottom:-3px; vertical-align:middle" type="text" /> to <iproformula alt=" " src="geteq.ashx?eqtext=~d\" style="margin-bottom:-3px; vertical-align:middle" type="text" /> is at most <iproformula alt=" " src="geteq.ashx?eqtext=~c\" style="margin-bottom:-3px; vertical-align:middle" type="text" />.</p>
			<p><iproelement_short correct="2" elid="2" format="" id="@step.s@id" size="2" tolerance="0.0" type="numeric" version="2" /> The distance from <iproformula alt=" " src="geteq.ashx?eqtext=a" style="margin-bottom:-3px; vertical-align:middle" type="text" /> to <iproformula alt=" " src="geteq.ashx?eqtext=~y\" style="margin-bottom:-3px; vertical-align:middle" type="text" /> is less than <iproformula alt=" " src="geteq.ashx?eqtext=@div{1;~x\}" style="margin-bottom:0px; vertical-align:middle" type="text" />.</p>
			<p><iproelement_short correct="5" elid="3" format="" id="@step.s@id" size="2" tolerance="0.0" type="numeric" version="2" /> <iproformula alt=" " src="geteq.ashx?eqtext=a" style="margin-bottom:-3px; vertical-align:middle" type="text" /> lies between <iproformula alt=" " src="geteq.ashx?eqtext=~b\" style="margin-bottom:-3px; vertical-align:middle" type="text" /> and <iproformula alt=" " src="geteq.ashx?eqtext=~a\" style="margin-bottom:-3px; vertical-align:middle" type="text" />.</p>
			<p><iproelement_short correct="1" elid="4" format="" id="@step.s@id" size="2" tolerance="0.0" type="numeric" version="2" /> <iproformula alt=" " src="geteq.ashx?eqtext=a" style="margin-bottom:-3px; vertical-align:middle" type="text" /> lies to the right of <iproformula alt=" " src="geteq.ashx?eqtext=~x\" style="margin-bottom:-3px; vertical-align:middle" type="text" />.</p>
			<p><iproelement_short correct="4" elid="5" format="" id="@step.s@id" size="2" tolerance="0.0" type="numeric" version="2" /> <iproformula alt=" " src="geteq.ashx?eqtext=a" style="margin-bottom:-3px; vertical-align:middle" type="text" /> lies to the left of <iproformula alt=" " src="geteq.ashx?eqtext=-~y\" style="margin-bottom:-3px; vertical-align:middle" type="text" /> or to the right of <iproformula alt=" " src="geteq.ashx?eqtext=~y\" style="margin-bottom:-3px; vertical-align:middle" type="text" />.</p>
			<p><iproelement_short correct="3" elid="6" format="" id="@step.s@id" size="2" tolerance="0.0" type="numeric" version="2" /> <iproformula alt=" " src="geteq.ashx?eqtext=a" style="margin-bottom:-3px; vertical-align:middle" type="text" /> is less than <iproformula alt=" " src="geteq.ashx?eqtext=~y\" style="margin-bottom:-3px; vertical-align:middle" type="text" /> units from <iproformula alt=" " src="geteq.ashx?eqtext=@div{1;~x\}" style="margin-bottom:-3px; vertical-align:middle" type="text" /></p>
			<p>&#160;</p>
		</div>
		<div><input class="next" hide="no" id="@step.next" onclick="javascript:next('next', '@step')" type="button" value="Check" /></div>
		<div><ipronav navtype="correct" stepid="step0corr" /><ipronav navtype="incorrect" stepid="step0inc" /></div>
	</iprostep>
	<iprostep id="step0corr">
		<div class="correct"> Correct feedback </div>
	</iprostep>
	<iprostep id="step0inc">
		<div class="incorrect"> Incorrect feedback</div>
	</iprostep>
	<iprostep id="solution">
		<div>
			<p><strong>SOLUTION</strong></p>
			<p>On the numbers line, numbers greater than <iproformula alt=" " src="geteq.ashx?eqtext=~x\" style="margin-bottom:-3px; vertical-align:middle" type="text" /> appear to the right; hence <iproformula alt=" " src="geteq.ashx?eqtext=a &amp;gt; ~x\" style="margin-bottom:-3px; vertical-align:middle" type="text" /> is equivalent to a number to the right of <iproformula alt=" " src="geteq.ashx?eqtext=~x\" style="margin-bottom:-3px; vertical-align:middle" type="text" />.</p>
			<p>&#160;</p>
			<p><iproformula alt=" " src="geteq.ashx?eqtext=@abs{a-~y\}" style="margin-bottom:-3px; vertical-align:middle" type="text" /> mesaures the distance from <iproformula alt=" " src="geteq.ashx?eqtext=a" style="margin-bottom:-3px; vertical-align:middle" type="text" /> to <iproformula alt=" " src="geteq.ashx?eqtext=~y\" style="margin-bottom:-3px; vertical-align:middle" type="text" />; hence <iproformula alt=" " src="geteq.ashx?eqtext= @abs{a-~y\} &amp;lt; @DIV{1;~x\}" style="margin-bottom:2px; vertical-align:middle" type="text" /> is satisfied by those numbers that are less than <iproformula alt=" " src="geteq.ashx?eqtext=@DIV{1;~x\}" style="margin-bottom:0px; vertical-align:middle" type="text" /> from <iproformula alt=" " src="geteq.ashx?eqtext=~y\" style="margin-bottom:-3px; vertical-align:middle" type="text" />.</p>
			<p>&#160;</p>
			<p><iproformula alt=" " src="geteq.ashx?eqtext=@abs{a-@DIV{1;~x\}}" style="margin-bottom:2px; vertical-align:middle" type="text" /> measures the distance from <iproformula alt=" " src="geteq.ashx?eqtext=a" style="margin-bottom:-3px; vertical-align:middle" type="text" /> to <iproformula alt=" " src="geteq.ashx?eqtext=@DIV{1;~x\}" style="margin-bottom:0px; vertical-align:middle" type="text" />; hence <iproformula alt=" " src="geteq.ashx?eqtext=@abs{a-@DIV{1;~x\}} &amp;lt; ~y\" style="margin-bottom:2px; vertical-align:middle" type="text" /> is satisfied by those numbers that are less than <iproformula alt=" " src="geteq.ashx?eqtext=~y\" style="margin-bottom:-3px; vertical-align:middle" type="text" /> units from <iproformula alt=" " src="geteq.ashx?eqtext=@DIV{1;~x\}" style="margin-bottom:0px; vertical-align:middle" type="text" />.</p>
			<p>&#160;</p>
			<p>The inequality <iproformula alt=" " src="geteq.ashx?eqtext=@abs{a} &amp;gt; ~y\" style="margin-bottom:-3px; vertical-align:middle" type="text" /> is equivalent to <iproformula alt=" " src="geteq.ashx?eqtext=a &amp;gt; ~y\" style="margin-bottom:-3px; vertical-align:middle" type="text" /> or <iproformula alt=" " src="geteq.ashx?eqtext= a &amp;lt; -~y\" style="margin-bottom:-3px; vertical-align:middle" type="text" />; that is <iproformula alt=" " src="geteq.ashx?eqtext=a" style="margin-bottom:-3px; vertical-align:middle" type="text" /> lies to the right of <iproformula alt=" " src="geteq.ashx?eqtext=~y\" style="margin-bottom:-3px; vertical-align:middle" type="text" /> or to the left of <iproformula alt=" " src="geteq.ashx?eqtext=-~y\" style="margin-bottom:-3px; vertical-align:middle" type="text" />.</p>
			<p>&#160;</p>
			<p>The interval described by the inequality <iproformula alt=" " src="geteq.ashx?eqtext=@abs{a-~z\} &amp;lt; ~x\" style="margin-bottom:-3px; vertical-align:middle" type="text" /> has a center at <iproformula alt=" " src="geteq.ashx?eqtext=~z\" style="margin-bottom:-3px; vertical-align:middle" type="text" /> and a radius of <iproformula alt=" " src="geteq.ashx?eqtext=~x\" style="margin-bottom:-3px; vertical-align:middle" type="text" />; that is the interval of those numbers between <iproformula alt=" " src="geteq.ashx?eqtext=~b\" style="margin-bottom:-3px; vertical-align:middle" type="text" /> and <iproformula alt=" " src="geteq.ashx?eqtext=~a\" style="margin-bottom:-3px; vertical-align:middle" type="text" />.</p>
			<p>&#160;</p>
			<p>The interval described by the inequality <iproformula alt=" " src="geteq.ashx?eqtext= 1 &amp;lt; a &amp;lt; ~y\" style="margin-bottom:-3px; vertical-align:middle" type="text" /> has a center at <iproformula alt=" " src="geteq.ashx?eqtext=~d\" style="margin-bottom:-3px; vertical-align:middle" type="text" /> and a radius of <iproformula alt=" " src="geteq.ashx?eqtext=~c\" style="margin-bottom:-3px; vertical-align:middle" type="text" />; that is the interval of those numbers that are less than <iproformula alt=" " src="geteq.ashx?eqtext=~c\" style="margin-bottom:-3px; vertical-align:middle" type="text" /> units from <iproformula alt=" " src="geteq.ashx?eqtext=~d\" style="margin-bottom:-3px; vertical-align:middle" type="text" />.</p>
			<p>&#160;</p>
		</div>
	</iprostep>
</iproblem>
